Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:39.84,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,All pirates who seek One Piece\Nstrive to reach the second half of the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:42.44,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The place called the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.71,0:02:51.15,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,However, the only one who ever conquered that ocean\Nwas the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:57.44,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The New World has killed\Nthe dreams and ambitions of countless pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:03.36,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,And now, the boy who ate the Gomu Gomu Fruit\Nand became a rubber man,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:07.12,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nare going to challenge that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:11.37,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:21.24,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,After a fierce battle, the Straw Hat Pirates\Nhave finally entered the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:24.08,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,the strongest sea, ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.08,0:03:28.56,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The crew has landed on Punk Hazard,\Nan island split between fire and ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:32.40,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,There they learned about the plans of Caesar Clown, \Nthe master of this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:34.69,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,While running from his weapon of mass destruction, \Nthe Land of Death,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:38.44,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,along with their ally, \NLaw of the Seven Warlords of the Sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:45.03,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,they put in motion their plan to kidnap Caesar, \Nsave the children and escape from the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:46.84,Main,Konbu,0,0,0,,Gimme the candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:47.85,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:48.91,Main,Konbu,0,0,0,,Gimme!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:51.02,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,No!  You can't have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:54.96,Main,Konbu,0,0,0,,Shut up!  Just give us the candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:57.22,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,How could she be so stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:03:59.20,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Don't do it!  Spit it all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:00.65,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Mocha, can you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:02.62,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mocha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:07.18,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I told you what that drug was, didn't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:09.93,Main,Gasmask Soldier,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:20.41,Main,Gasmask Soldier,0,0,0,,Straw Hat Luffy!  What's he doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.41,0:04:22.28,Main,Gasmask Soldier,0,0,0,,Shoot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:27.74,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Where is Caesar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:30.29,Main,Gasmask Soldier,0,0,0,,I dunno!  I don't{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:36.25,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Where is Caesar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:50.57,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The killer gas, Land of Death,\Nhas leaked into Laboratory Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:55.96,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,It is now flowing into Building B, where\Nthe Straw Hats, Navy's G-5 unit, and children are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:01.69,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,You're going the wrong way.  Turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:02.99,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:07.77,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,That damn gas is trying to cut us off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:09.62,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,You just keep going the wrong way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:14.00,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Stay still, you little brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:17.27,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Give them the shots quickly, G-5!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:18.76,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,We're almost done, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:20.96,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Hang in there, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:23.01,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,C-Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:29.60,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Hey, hurry it up, Raccoon Dog!\NWe don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:31.40,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Don't give up, Mocha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:34.31,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:38.75,Main,Kin'emon,0,0,0,,M-Momonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:42.86,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Kin'emon-san!  You're headed straight for the gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:02.03,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,This is where my men should be,\Nbut there's no one here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:10.07,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,What was that creepy room?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:15.18,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.93,0:06:19.73,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,I can hear something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:20.86,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Or do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:26.78,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,Master, isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:28.73,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,Look, it's Brownbeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.73,0:06:31.66,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,I thought he'd been captured by Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:33.47,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,Guess he made it after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:34.87,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:07:00.37,Thoughts,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,The Surveillance Snail is active!  That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:03.26,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Soldiers of Punk Hazard, please listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:05.88,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,You must be watching this somewhere, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:08.53,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,You're all being deceived!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:13.99,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Everything Caesar has told you is a lie!  You'll all be killed if you stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:16.21,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,What's he on about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:19.35,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,Did he go mad after being captured by Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:23.15,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,Brownbeard is right below us,\Non the first floor of Building R.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:29.34,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,According to Master's plan, the Straw Hats and the marines should be there soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:31.55,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,Should we call Brownbeard up to the second floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:35.30,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Let me tell you who Caesar really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:38.52,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,No.  I will go down to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:40.14,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,Then we're going with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:52.07,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:56.59,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Oh, my loyal subordinate, Brownbeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:08:00.41,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you managed to escape from Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.27,0:08:03.09,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:07.19,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,You're covered in bruises!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:08.34,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:12.38,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Oh my, you seem to be in a rather foul mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:15.47,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:19.14,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Return my men to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.61,0:08:24.05,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,We were attacked and robbed\Nat the center of the island, but they weren't dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:25.72,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,They should be back here by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:29.19,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,Hey, he's provoking Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:31.77,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Hmm?  Your men?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:33.32,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:43.50,Flashbacks,Centaur,0,0,0,,Master!  Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:47.46,Flashbacks,Caesar,0,0,0,,What?  Oh, Brownbeard's men?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:52.57,Flashbacks,Centaur,0,0,0,,Master, there are marines by the front gate,\Nand the doors are closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:55.68,Flashbacks,Centaur,0,0,0,,We can't get inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:56.84,Flashbacks,Centaur,0,0,0,,Please, help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:09:01.74,Flashbacks,Caesar,0,0,0,,I see, that's terrible!  I'll take care of it\Nright away!  Stay where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:04.77,Flashbacks,Centaur,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:06.98,Flashbacks,Centaur,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:10.85,Flashbacks,Monet,0,0,0,,Master, how do you plan to let them in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:20.62,Flashbacks,Caesar,0,0,0,,Just leave them.\NThe Land of Death will reach them soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:27.13,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,I wonder, what happened to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:29.11,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,I haven't heard from them for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:34.00,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,If they haven't returned,\Nthen that must mean they're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:44.39,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Are you worried?  Well, I guess you would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:47.56,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,If they were outside, the Land of Death\Nwould have killed them long ago, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:49.90,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:52.50,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:55.21,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing, Brownbeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.56,0:10:06.29,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,Brownbeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:10.06,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,I can never trust you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:12.30,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,What's gotten into him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:14.34,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,What did he just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:18.76,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,You're my friends, too.\NWe've lived on this island for two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:20.72,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,You have to get off the island right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:24.50,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Do you know what this man\Nhas been calling you behind your backs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:26.10,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,I'll tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:30.19,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,This is what he called you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:33.16,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Ginnafibs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:36.16,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Ginnig...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:40.74,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,G-Ginns...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.74,0:10:44.04,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,G-G-ggigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:49.46,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Brownbeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.74,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,Speak up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.74,0:10:53.25,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,Is that meant to be some sort of spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:56.26,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,What a funny guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.81,0:10:58.51,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Ginnigigg!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:00.40,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:07.31,Flashbacks,Caesar,0,0,0,,They will continue to obey me,\Nbelieving that I am their god of salvation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:11.48,Flashbacks,Caesar,0,0,0,,They're merely being kept alive\Nso I can use them as human guinea pigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:13.77,Thoughts,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,He called you guinea-pigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.49,0:11:19.28,Thoughts,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,What's this?!  My mouth won't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:23.57,Thoughts,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,You did something to me, didn't you, Caesar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:46.51,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,What is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:48.53,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,What sort of play is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.91,0:11:53.81,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:56.19,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,This is a muscle relaxant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:59.30,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,You can no longer speak, let alone move around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:08.99,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Oh right.  I just remembered, Brownbeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:12.56,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,About your former men, I remembered...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:13.87,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,that I abandoned them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:24.99,Thoughts,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,You... damn freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:30.14,Thoughts,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,How... How {\i1}dare{\i0} you kill my men?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:45.36,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Oh, and while we're on the subject...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:47.78,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,I guess I'll tell you one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:58.59,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,The weapon malfunction\Nthat left everyone near death four years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:06.84,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,That was my doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:23.07,Thoughts,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,It wasn't Vegapunk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:27.49,Thoughts,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,So you almost killed them all yourself,\Nand then just {\i1}pretended{\i0} to save them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:44.81,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Hey, stop!  You have to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.81,0:13:48.09,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Please help me!  Brownbeard has gone mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:57.14,Thoughts,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,This island was made into hell on earth\Nby Caesar himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:14:01.90,Thoughts,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Run!  He is a devil disguised as a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:03.44,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,Hey, Brownbeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:05.11,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,What are you doing to our savior?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:12.67,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Oh no!  Brownbeard is dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.67,0:14:17.04,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,We're too late!\NStraw Hat must have messed with his brain somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:19.08,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,Brownbeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:22.46,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Shoot!  You must shoot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:24.34,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,You're all in danger here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:28.13,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:10.19,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,And here comes the killing blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:12.43,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Gastan{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:54.42,Main,Momonosuke,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:57.14,Main,Momonosuke,0,0,0,,Are we out of the hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:58.27,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:01.39,Main,Momonosuke,0,0,0,,So you successfully climbed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:03.55,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:25.04,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,And here comes the killing blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:26.75,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Momo, get out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:29.63,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Gastan{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:42.18,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:45.57,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Th-That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:46.90,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,It grazed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:49.57,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Shit!  Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:20.49,Main,Gasmask soldiers,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's Straw Hat... Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:05.83,Flashbacks,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Just like them,\Nmy life was also saved by Master's kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:09.89,Flashbacks,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Master is the kind-hearted god of salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:15.86,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,G-Get back to the second floor, my men!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:19.02,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats and the Navy should be here any moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:20.32,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Prepare to resume the experiment!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:20.99,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:23.79,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,Make sure all our brokers get the footage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:26.99,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:33.89,Flashbacks,Caesar,0,0,0,,All of them will probably be dead within five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:39.19,Flashbacks,Caesar,0,0,0,,Then we'll have to gather some more kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:42.89,Main,Momonosuke,0,0,0,,Luffy!  That is him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:45.56,Main,Momonosuke,0,0,0,,He is the one\Nwho caused the kind-hearted children to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:47.81,Main,Momonosuke,0,0,0,,Who caused them to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:49.91,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:56.28,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,You've tricked everyone here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.29,0:19:00.03,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,What is this island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:10.36,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Ah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:13.46,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,I guess I could tell you, you poor, ignorant fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:15.25,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,I'll tell you the secret of this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:17.07,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,We're not broadcasting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:18.28,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:19.20,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,Checking the signal strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:20.43,Main,Gasmask soldier,0,0,0,,Get it running!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.15,0:19:29.85,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,This place is like gas or air.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:33.61,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,A seemingly non-existent island!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:34.82,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:44.18,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Listen up, this island shouldn't exist, and yet it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:47.73,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,That is why it has such close ties to the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:50.74,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,This is a base of underworld science.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.40,0:19:57.88,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,I can perform illegal experiments or obtain experimental subjects.  I'm free to do whatever I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:03.12,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,I have powerful backers that completely erase everything that happens from the records!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:05.76,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Officially, nothing never happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:14.56,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,No matter how much you cry or whine, no help will ever come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:19.53,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,You know nothing about this island, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:24.78,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,If you go off half-cocked and interfere here,\Nyou won't live to tell the tale!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:27.24,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,The same goes for your alliance with Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:30.94,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,He's trying to interfere with the SAD production.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.94,0:20:36.40,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who can make it, so he's using you to kidnap me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.44,0:20:40.49,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,You see, Straw Hat, the thing about SAD...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.49,0:20:46.98,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,At the factory owned by Donquixote Doflamingo,\Nthe most dangerous member of the Seven Warlords,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:50.27,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,it is transformed into a fruit called Smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.67,0:20:55.70,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Do you know what Smile is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.70,0:20:57.38,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,We have...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.38,0:21:00.61,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,successfully created Devil Fruits!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:05.87,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Smiles are artificially created Zoan-type Devil Fruits!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:10.66,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,It's a fruit that anyone seeking strength would want to get their hands on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:18.96,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Doflamingo is using the Smiles\Nto make deals with the big shots in the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:27.46,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,I heard that one of the Four Emperors is already using them to form an army of hundreds of Devil Fruit users!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:32.13,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,It sends chills down your spine, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.49,0:21:36.65,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Now do you understand what you're meddling with?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:43.99,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Do you see how many big shots you'd piss off by interfering with Doflamingo's business?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.64,0:21:48.62,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,If those big shots move against you, the world itself will tremble!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.62,0:21:52.80,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,And Law is trying to make that happen.  The fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.80,0:21:56.29,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Someone at your level\Nwould be completely obliterated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.22,0:22:01.31,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,You can try to capture me, but I am protected!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.31,0:22:04.31,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,By Doflamingo!  By the Four Emperors!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.31,0:22:07.97,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Do you have the guts to pick a fight with them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.25,0:22:13.68,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Of course you don't!\NSo if you're gonna run, then now's your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.11,0:22:17.40,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Get out my sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.22,0:22:26.36,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,A fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:47.99,Main,Momonosuke,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.42,0:23:00.85,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I've picked {\i1}plenty{\i0} of fights like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.40,0:23:12.27,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Completely unaffected\Nby the power of the Gas Gas Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.27,0:23:15.51,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Luffy's enraged fists drive Caesar into a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.51,0:23:19.75,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Smoker faces Vergo's powerful Haki,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.75,0:23:24.56,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,and the overwhelming disadvantage leaves him on the verge of death!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.56,0:23:25.88,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:27.25,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,The Shocking Conclusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.25,0:23:28.84,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Smoker VS Vergo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.84,0:23:30.68,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
